node.title: Search for woman missing in river continues
node.description: Land search and rescue staff are scouring the ManawatÅ« River in kayaks, looking for any sign of the 27-year-old woman.
node.content:
["The search for a swimmer missing in the Manawatū River is continuing without the police dive squad.", "", "
Land search and rescue staff are scouring the Manawatū River for a 27-year-old woman who entered the water on Wednesday. Photo: 123RF
", "Land search and rescue staff are scouring the river on kayaks as they look for a 27-year-old woman who entered the water in Palmerston North on Wednesday.", "Yesterday the body of an 11-year-old girl who also went underwater on Wednesday was found.", "The river was high on Wednesday after overnight rain."]
